.env
*.env
!.env.example

# Org / checkout configs (credentials, card data, PII)
good360_orgs_master.json
good360_checkout_config.json
reviving_homes_config.json
reviving_homes_checkout_config.json
hope4humanity_config.json
*_config.json
!*.example.json

# Bot tokens and credentials
*_token.txt
*_credentials.json
*.pem
*.key

# === STATE & RUNTIME ARTIFACTS ===
# State files (regenerated by system)
